{{Quote|The Queen and I will sign a treaty that will legitimize our occupation here.|Nute Gunray to [[Sio Bibble/Legends|Sio Bibble]]|<ref name="Episode 1">{{Film|I}}</ref>}}
The '''Free Trade Petition''' was a document drafted by the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] in order to lift [[Senate Resolution BR-0371]] and stop the taxation of the [[Free Trade Zone/Legends|Free Trade Zone]] so the Federation could continue their militarization.

{{Stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Most likely this was part of the "treaty" that [[Viceroy of the Trade Federation/Legends|Viceroy]] [[Nute Gunray/Legends|Gunray]] wanted [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|the Queen]] to sign, along with her making Naboo a Federation protectorate, thus allowing their troops' presence.

